{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","kind":"attribute","text":"MainActor"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSSwitchItem"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"Layouts","level":2,"text":"Layouts"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The component can be rendered as two different layouts:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"default","type":"text"}]},{"text":": the component has a leading indicator, a label and optional helper texts, and an optional trailing decorative icon","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"inverse"}]},{"type":"text","text":": like the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}]},{"type":"text","text":" layout but with a trailing switch indicator and a leading optional decorative icon"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Indicator-states","level":2,"text":"Indicator states"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The switch indicator has two available states set as a boolean property that determines whether the toggle is on or off."}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Particular-cases","level":2,"text":"Particular cases"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem"},{"type":"text","text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look and feel is implemented for that if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is risen."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"In addition, the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem"},{"type":"text","text":" can be in read only mode, i.e. the user cannot interact with the component yet but this component must not be considered"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"as disabled."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The switch can be also outlined in some cases."}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","level":2,"text":"Accessibility considerations"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" will use several elements to describe the component: if component disabled \/ read only, if error context, the label and helper texts and a custom switch trait.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Forbidden-by-design","level":2,"text":"Forbidden by design"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a read only component."}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component."}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both a read only and a disabled component."}],"type":"strong"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Code-samples","level":2,"text":"Code samples"},{"code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an unselected state","    @Published var isOn: Bool = false","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(isOn: $isOn, label: \"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\")","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label, but in read only mode (user cannot interact yet, but not disabled).","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(isOn: $isOn, label: \"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isReadOnly: true)","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label, and an helper text.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(isOn: $isOn, label: \"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", helper: \"The Beatles\")","","    \/\/ A leading switch with an additional label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(isOn: $isOn, label: \"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", additionalLabel: \"The Beatles\", helper: \"1967\")","","    \/\/ A trailing switch with a label, an additonal label, an helper text and an icon.","    \/\/ The inverse layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(isOn: $isOn,","                  label: \"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\",","                  additionalLabel: \"The Beatles\",","                  helper: \"1967\",","                  isReversed: true,","                  icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"))","","    \/\/ A trailing switch with a label, an helper text, an icon, a divider and is about an error.","    \/\/ The inverse layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(isOn: $isOn,","                  label: \"Rescue from this world!\",","                  helper: \"Put your hand in mine\",","                  icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"),","                  isReversed: true,","                  isError: true,","                  hasDivider: true)","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label, but disabled.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(isOn: $isOn, label: \"Rescue from this world!\")","        .disabled(true)","","    \/\/ Never disable a read only or an error-related switch as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSSwitchItem(isOn: $isOn, label: \"Kaboom!\", isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error","    OUDSSwitchItem(isOn: $isOn, label: \"Kaboom!\", isReadyOnly: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Design-documentation","level":2,"text":"Design documentation"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.14.0"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside","style":"note","name":"Since"}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsswitchitem"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem"},"metadata":{"title":"OUDSSwitchItem","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSSwitchItem"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents14OUDSSwitchItemV","roleHeading":"Structure","modules":[{"name":"OUDSComponents"}],"symbolKind":"struct","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSSwitchItem"}]},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem"},{"text":" proposes layouts to add in your views some swith components.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If you want to use a switch with only an indicator, prefer instead ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitch"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"topicSections":[{"anchor":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem\/init(isOn:label:helper:icon:flipIcon:isReversed:isError:isReadOnly:hasDivider:)"],"generated":true,"title":"Initializers"},{"anchor":"Instance-Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem\/body"],"generated":true,"title":"Instance Properties"},{"anchor":"Default-Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem\/View-Implementations"],"generated":true,"title":"Default Implementations"}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"references":{"https://unified-design-system.orange.com/":{"identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/","titleInlineContent":[{"text":"unified-design-system.orange.com","type":"text"}],"url":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/","type":"link","title":"unified-design-system.orange.com"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSSwitchItem/body":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsswitchitem\/body","abstract":[],"title":"body","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"body"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"some"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:7SwiftUI4ViewP","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"View"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem\/body"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSSwitchItem":{"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsswitchitem","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem"},{"type":"text","text":" proposes layouts to add in your views some swith components."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If you want to use a switch with only an indicator, prefer instead "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitch"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSSwitchItem"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSSwitchItem"}],"title":"OUDSSwitchItem","type":"topic"},"doc://OUDSComponents/s8SendableP":{"title":"Swift.Sendable","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","type":"unresolvable"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSSwitchItem/View-Implementations":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsswitchitem\/view-implementations","abstract":[],"type":"topic","title":"View Implementations","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem\/View-Implementations","role":"collectionGroup","kind":"article"},"doc://OUDSComponents/7SwiftUI4ViewP":{"title":"SwiftUICore.View","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP","type":"unresolvable"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents":{"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The catalog of all components provided by OUDS. It contains also "},{"code":"View","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" extensions and "},{"code":"ViewModifiers","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to apply tokens and styles on components and higher-level views."}],"type":"topic","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents","title":"OUDSComponents","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSSwitch":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitch"},{"type":"text","text":" prop